  </footer>
    <div class="particles">
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
      <div class="particle"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="top-flex-wrapper">
        <div class="glass-card">
          <div class="progress-container">
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill" id="progressFill"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="step-indicator">
              <span class="step active" id="step1">Register now</span>
              <span class="step" id="step2">Project details</span>
              <span class="step" id="step3">Confirm</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <form id="multiForm">
            <div class="form-step active" data-step="1">
              <h2 class="form-title">
              Join the world of doers
              </h2>
              
              <p class="form-subtitle">
                Register for more efficiency within your team. We just need some basic information to get you started.
                
              </p>
              
              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label">E-mail*</label>
                <input
                  type="email"
                  class="form-input"
                  name="email"
                  placeholder="din@email.com"
                  required
                />
              </div>
             <div class="form-group">
  <label class="form-label">Password *</label>
  <input
    type="password"
    class="form-input"
    name="password"
    id="password"
    placeholder="Create a secure password"
    required
    minlength="8"
    autocomplete="new-password"
  />
</div>
              <div class="form-group">
  <label class="form-label">Confirm Password *</label>
  <input
    type="password"
    class="form-input"
    name="confirmPassword"
    id="confirmPassword"
    placeholder="Confirm your password"
    required
    minlength="8"
    autocomplete="new-password"
  />
</div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label">What is your role within the team?</label>
                <select class="form-select" name="role">
                  <option value="">Choose your role</option>
                  <option value="product-owner">Project Manager</option>
                  <option value="scrum-master">Scrum Master</option>
                  <option value="developer">Developer</option>
                  <option value="designer">Designer</option>
                  <option value="tester">Tester/QA</option>
                  <option value="stakeholder">Stakeholder</option>
                  <option value="student">Student</option>
                  <option value="other">Other</option>
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-step" data-step="2">
              <h2 class="form-title">Project Information</h2>
              <p class="form-subtitle">
                Describe the project's purpose, its main goals, and the results you expect. Please also specify the key features or deliverables
              </p>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label"
                  >What type of project? *</label
                >
                <div class="radio-group">
                  <div class="radio-item">
                    <input
                      type="radio"
                      id="daily"
                      name="meetingType"
                      value="daily"
                      required
                    />
                    <label for="daily">Agile</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="radio-item">
                    <input
                      type="radio"
                      id="planning"
                      name="meetingType"
                      value="planning"
                    />
                    <label for="planning">Productlaunch</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="radio-item">
                    <input
                      type="radio"
                      id="review"
                      name="meetingType"
                      value="review"
                    />
                    <label for="review">Maintanance</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="radio-item">
                    <input
                      type="radio"
                      id="retro"
                      name="meetingType"
                      value="retro"
                    />
                    <label for="retro">Merger</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="radio-item">
                    <input
                      type="radio"
                      id="refinement"
                      name="meetingType"
                      value="refinement"
                    />
                    <label for="refinement">Backlog Refinement</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label">Timezone</label>
                <div class="checkbox-group">
                  <div class="checkbox-item">
                    <input
                      type="checkbox"
                      id="morning"
                      name="availability[]"
                      value="morning"
                    />
                    <label for="morning">New York</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox-item">
                    <input
                      type="checkbox"
                      id="afternoon"
                      name="availability[]"
                      value="afternoon"
                    />
                    <label for="afternoon">Berlin</label>
                  </div>
                  <div class="checkbox-item">
                    <input
                      type="checkbox"
                      id="evening"
                      name="availability[]"
                      value="evening"
                    />
                    <label for="evening">Tokyo</label>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label">Size of project</label>
                <select class="form-select" name="projectSize">
                  <option value="">Define Project Scope</option>
                  <option value="small">Small project (1-2 weeks)</option>
                  <option value="medium">Medium project (2 months or more)</option>
                  <option value="large">Large project (3-6 months or more)</option>
                  <option value="enterprise"
                    >Enterprise project (6+ months)</option
                  >
                </select>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-step" data-step="3">
              <h2 class="form-title">Confirm & Join us</h2>
              <p class="form-subtitle">
                Time for kickoff.
              </p>
              <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label"></label>
                <textarea
                  class="form-textarea"
                  name="message"
                  placeholder="Motivate your teammates with an inspirational start..."
                ></textarea>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <div class="checkbox-item">
                  <input type="checkbox" id="terms" name="terms" required />
                  <label for="terms"
                    >I agree to the general terms and conditions of purchase *</label
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <div class="checkbox-item">
                  <input
                    type="checkbox"
                    id="notifications"
                    name="notifications"
                  />
                  <label for="notifications"
                    >Yes I want weekly tips & tricks sent to my email
                    </label
                  >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-step" data-step="success" id="successStep">
              <div class="success-message">
                <div class="success-icon">
                  <svg
                    class="success-icon-svg"
                    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                    fill="none"
                    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                    stroke-width="1.5"
                    stroke="currentColor"
                  >
                    <path
                      stroke-linecap="round"
                      stroke-linejoin="round"
                      d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                    />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <h2 class="success-title">Welcome to the club of doers</h2>
                <p class="success-text">
                  Welcome to the Team!
Thank you for registering and creating your project with us. We're excited to have you on board!

We've received your project details and a member of our team will be in touch shortly to review your needs and get the ball rolling.


                  <br /><br />
                  <strong>In the meantime:</strong> feel free to explore our platform. You can find helpful guides in our Knowledge Base and connect with other users in the Community Forum.

If you have any questions, don't hesitate to reach out. We're here to help you succeed.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="button-group" id="buttonGroup">
              <button
                type="button"
                class="btn btn-secondary"
                id="prevBtn"
                style="display: none;"
              >
                Previous
              </button>
              <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" id="nextBtn"
                >Next step</button
              >
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
        <div class="why-choose-us-heading">
          <h3 class="section-title">Why use our service?</h3>
           <p class="main-text">
            In a world drowning in digital noise and disorganized chaos, a new dawn of productivity has arrived. The team behind Weee.. has done it again and developed a Project Manager Tool that isn't just a software; it's a revolution, it´s the future. It´s Weee...DidIT It's the silent hero working behind the scenes, transforming your chaotic to-do lists into a perfectly orchestrated symphony of success.
          </p>
          <div class="form-logo-container">
  <img src="/logo.png" alt="Företagslogotyp" class="form-logo" />
 <p class="main-text"> Nike say´s Just Do It. We on Weee always say WeDidIT </p>
</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="why-choose-us">
        <div class="features-grid">
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
