              </svg>
            </div>
            <h4 class="feature-title">Faster Delivery</h4>
            <p class="feature-description">
              Say goodbye to distractions. Our dynamic daily standups and sprint goals act as your team's North Star, meticulously aligning every effort to your most critical priorities and keeping everyone perfectly in sync.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-icon">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
